<section class="founder" data-screen-label="Founder note">
  <div class="founder__inner">
    <div class="founder__photo reveal"><img src="/assets/photos/team-rich-scherf.png" alt="Rich Scherf, founder of Cardo" loading="lazy" /></div>
    <div class="founder__body reveal">
      <p class="eyebrow">A note from our founder</p>
      <blockquote class="founder__quote">"I started Cardo in 2013 to run San Diego homes the way I'd want my own run — designed well, accounted for honestly, and cared for like it matters. Fourteen years later, that's still the whole job."</blockquote>
      <p>We stayed small on purpose. Every owner has a real person they can call, every home is held to a standard we'd accept ourselves, and nothing about the work gets handed off to a stranger.</p>
      <div class="founder__sig"><b>Rich Scherf</b><span>Founder &amp; CEO, Cardo Vacation Rentals</span></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
